  "keyFeatures": [
    "Modularity (AbpModule, dependency graph, lifecycle contributors)",
    "Dependency Injection with conventional registration and property injection",
    "DDD building blocks: Entity, AggregateRoot, Repository, DomainService, ValueObject",
    "Application Services layer with CRUD AppService base classes",
    "Unit of Work and transaction orchestration (Volo.Abp.Uow)",
    "Data filtering (soft delete, multi-tenant) and data seeding",
    "Entity Framework Core integration with SQL Server, PostgreSQL, MySQL, Oracle, SQLite",
    "MongoDB, Dapper, MemoryDb persistence",
    "Multi-tenancy resolution and Tenant Management module",
    "Caching (in-memory, Redis distributed)",
    "Distributed locking (Medallion, Dapr)",
    "Local and Distributed Event Bus (RabbitMQ, Kafka, Azure Service Bus, Dapr, Rebus)",
    "Background Jobs (default, Hangfire, Quartz, RabbitMQ, TickerQ) and Background Workers",
    "Auditing (auditing module + entity change history)",
    "Authorization, Permission Management, Roles",
    "Feature Management and Global Features",
    "Setting Management",
    "Object mapping (AutoMapper, Mapperly, LuckyPenny)",
    "Object Extending and Multi-Lingual Objects",
    "Validation (built-in + FluentValidation)",
    "Specifications pattern",
    "BLOB Storing (FileSystem, Azure, AWS, Google, Aliyun, Minio, Bunny, in-memory, database)",
    "Emailing + MailKit and SMS (Aliyun, Tencent Cloud)",
    "Imaging (ImageSharp, SkiaSharp, Magick.NET) + ASP.NET Core imaging",
    "Virtual File System and Text Templating (Razor, Scriban)",
    "Localization core + abstractions and Multi-Lingual Objects",
    "Timing (IClock, time zones)",
    "JSON abstractions with System.Text.Json and Newtonsoft providers",
    "GDPR abstractions",
    "AI abstractions and Volo.Abp.AI integrations",
    "ASP.NET Core MVC pipeline: conventions, model binding, exception handling, anti-forgery, validation, view features",
    "Dynamic HTTP API conventions and dynamic JS / TS client proxy generation",
    "Identity Model client (token storage, auto refresh)",
    "Remote Services and HTTP client proxies",
    "Swashbuckle integration with ABP conventions",
    "JWT Bearer, OAuth, OpenID Connect authentication",
    "SignalR integration",
    "Serilog integration",
    "MVC UI: Bootstrap theme shared, theme basic, bundling, widgets, navigation, packages",
    "Blazor: Server, WebAssembly, MAUI Blazor, theming, MudBlazor, Blazorise, bundling",
    "Angular packages: core, OAuth, schematics, generators, theme-shared/basic, identity, account, permission-management, feature-management, setting-management, tenant-management, cms-kit",
    "MAUI client + WPF startup template",
    "Identity, Account, OpenIddict, IdentityServer modules",
    "Permission, Setting, Feature, Tenant management modules",
    "Audit Logging, Background Jobs, BLOB Storing Database modules",
    "CMS Kit, Docs, Blogging content modules",
    "Basic Theme, Virtual File Explorer, Client Simulation",
    "Users subpackage (shared user abstractions)",
    "ABP CLI: new, build, update, install-libs, generate-proxy, bundle, login, source, translate, prompt, MCP",
    "Project Building, Project Modification, Service Proxying CLI subsystems",
    "Startup templates: app, app-nolayers, console, module, maui, wpf",
    "ABP Test Base infrastructure",
    "PowerShell build & deploy pipeline (build/, deploy/)",
    "NuGet & localization tooling"
  ],
